1. High-Level Architecture
| Service                  | Language         | Responsibility                                     |
| ------------------------ | ---------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| **Payment Service**      | Go               | Payment processing, idempotency, external gateways |
| **Subscription Service** | Java             | Plans, lifecycle, upgrades/downgrades              |
| **Billing Service**      | Python           | Invoicing, proration, tax, currency                |
| **API Gateway**          | (optional)       | Routing, auth                                      |
| **Message Broker**       | (Kafka/RabbitMQ) | Async communication                                |
| **PostgreSQL**           | DB               | Shared persistence (or per-service schema)         |

2.Data Flow
Client → API Gateway
    → Subscription Service (create/update plan)
        → emits event: subscription.updated
            → Billing Service (generate invoice)
                → Payment Service (charge)
                    → emits payment.success / failure
                        → Billing updates invoice
